  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/thesmok">thesmok</a> 7 hours ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">As a citizen of a country currently defending in a war, unmanned systems are a literal lifesaver. We can send an armed robot where we previously would have to send a soldier. This is a good thing and before the war many had the same pacifist sentiment in the tech sector, but it&#x27;s completely reversed now.<p>Though I can understand your position being in a country that&#x27;s not defending itself currently.</div>
  
  <div class="replies-container" id="replies-47775715"></div>
</div>
